PART 4 â€” The 7 Emotional Design Principles (how to make it feel human)
Instant feedback: Every tap = response.
Predictability: No surprises. Always show next step.
Reassurance: Confirm success, never leave users unsure.
Forgiveness: Easy undo; errors donâ€™t feel fatal.
Delight: Subtle success animations â€” dopamine, not fireworks.
Transparency: Show sync status, data saved state.
Empowerment: Users feel in control â€” not controlled.

